history.proof: intros a b l H. induction l as [| h t IH]. -- simpl in H. contradiction. -- simpl in H. destruct (Aeq_dec h b) as [Hb | Hb]. ++ apply IH in H. auto. ++ apply in_inv in H as [H1 | H2]. ** subst. intro H'. contradiction. ** apply IH in H2. auto.
